						               													<description>From the ad:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WAR OF THE AGES takes a quantum leap toward the chaos and derangement of warfare! Can you direct the charge of Julius Caesar&amp;rsquo;s Samurai warriors against Robert E. Lee and his loyal Vikings? This two player (or team) game consists of 124 cards which simulate the contest between many of the famous and infamous military leaders and forces from 2300BC to 1865. Each battlefield and the composition of each player&amp;rsquo;s forces will be created randomly or can be custom designed from the three decks of cards - A force deck, a leader deck, and a terrain deck. Each combat unit (a leader and force card together) is placed in a stand, with its orientation within the stand determining its mode (charge, hold, etc.) while also hiding its attributes from the other player. Relive military history as never before!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For more information, contact: raysmith@kuhncom.net&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
